                    <h2>Introduction</h2>
                    <p>Stress has now become the most used term in everyone’s life. We can observe everybody saying that I have stress for my exams, I have stress in my work, stress in daily life etc. Everyone faces the same problem that is “stress”.<br>We all want us to get relieve from all the stresses in our life but we are not able to get relief from stress. In this you case, you can do some activities, which will help you in getting relief from stress. So, in this article you will read what is stress, difference between stress and anxiety because there is a misconception between stress and anxiety and the 10 best stress-relieving activities.</p>
