                    <article>
                        <h3>Types of Stress</h3>
                        <h4 class="text-center centered-box">STRESS</h4>
                        <table>
                            <tr>
                                <th><h5>Acute Stress</h5></th>
                                <th><h5>Chronic Stress</h5></th>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td>Acute stress is the stress, which happens for a very short period loke for hours or some days.</td>
                                <td>Chronic stress is the stress, which happens for a longer period like for weeks or months.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td>Acute stress helps us to get rid of the problems of our life, by taking strress for shorter time and then taking valuble actions.</td>
                                <td>Chronic stress leads to serious health problems as it only makes us to over think a lot about a particular situation</td>
                            </tr>
                        </table>
