                        <h2>10 Best stress relieving activities</h2>
                        <p>Now, let us read the 10 best ways of relieving stress. By following, the activiteis you will surely help in geeting relieve from your stresses.</p>
                        <ol>
                            <li>
                                <section>
                                    <h3>Deep Breathing</h3>
                                    <p>Researchers have shown that deep breathing helps in stress reduction. By deep breathing, you take more oxygen in which makes our heart rate slower and the over; thinking of things also slows down.  Deep breathing directly affects our brain and makes us calmer. Thus, it helps a lot in stress relievement.</p>
                                    <figure class="image-container">
                                        <img src="/media/images/articles/2022/12/08/deep_breathing.jpg" alt="">
                                        <figcaption>Google Analytics</figcaption>
                                    </figure>
