                            <li>
                                <section>
                                    <h3>Listening to music</h3>
                                    <p>Music relaxes and calms down our mind and body. Researchers have shown that music especially classical music makes our nervous system calm and thus helps in reducing stress. You can listen to any classical music according to your choice to get relief from stress.</p>
                                    <figure class="image-container">
                                        <img src="/media/images/articles/2022/12/08/music.jpg" alt="">
                                        <figcaption>Google Analytics</figcaption>
                                    </figure>
