                                <section>
                                    <h3>Walking</h3>
                                    <p>Walking helps a lot in stress relievment, you can walk in a park, in neighboring place or in garden. Try to choose a place where you can find peace and beautiful scenery. Therefore, that it will refresh your mood and will automatically feel better and get relieve from stress.</p>
                                    <figure class="image-container">
                                        <img src="/media/images/articles/2022/12/08/walking.jpg" alt="">
                                        <figcaption>Google Analytics</figcaption>
                                    </figure>
                                </section>
