                                <section>
                                    <h3>Close eyes</h3>
                                    <p>Closing eyes makes our mind and muscles more relaxed. Close your eyes and just think about your present, do not think about your stress. Try to think positive about yourself and your life. Try to divert your mind from the stressor to positive things. You can also rub your palms together and give heat to your eyes using your palms; this will make you feel better.</p>
                                    <figure class="image-container">
                                        <img src="/media/images/articles/2022/12/08/close_eyes.jpg" alt="">
