                                <section>
                                    <h3>Meditate</h3>
                                    <p>Meditation is one of the best stress reliever. Meditation helps to focus at one place; it makes our mind to concentrate at a place rather than over thinking about different things. Daily you should practice meditation for 20-25 minutes or more according to your comfort.</p>
                                    <figure class="image-container">
                                        <img src="/media/images/articles/2022/12/08/meditate.jpg" alt="">
