                                <section>
                                    <h3>Laugh</h3>
                                    <p>Try to laugh in every situation of life. Laughing reduces your mental load and gives relieve from stress. Laughing helps to feel us happier and joyful. It also reduces our stress hormones. So, try to laugh more and more.</p>
                                    <figure class="image-container">
                                        <img src="/media/images/articles/2022/12/08/laugh.jpg" alt="">
