                                <section>
                                    <h3>Write</h3>
                                    <p>By writing, the things down you can get relief from your stress. Write down all the things by which you are feeling stressed. After writing them on a paper, you will feel relaxed and calmer. Writing helps you to know more about yourself.</p>
                                    <figure class="image-container">
                                        <img src="/media/images/articles/2022/12/08/write.jpg" alt="">
