                                <section>
                                    <h3>Talk</h3>
                                    <p>Talk with a person whom you can share your feelings or the reason of stress. By talking to someone you, can get some relieve from a lot of stress and feel better. You can talk to anyone your family members or friends whomever you want.</p>
