                                    <h3>Gratitude</h3>
                                    <p>When we express gratitude, our brain releases two hormones, i.e. Dopamine and Serotonin, which makes us, feel good. This helps in stress reduction. Show gratitude for what good you have in your life rather than thinking and regretting for what you do not have.</p>
